	C       class      yes     no      0      NONE   classes
	E       enum       yes     no      0      NONE   enumerators
	H       checker    yes     no      0      NONE   checkers
	I       interface  yes     no      0      NONE   interfaces
	K       package    yes     no      0      NONE   packages
